OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine end to the day, with bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Leading into a dry, warm
OL,8,Fand muggy night with variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud, clear spells and light
OL,10,Fwinds. Perhaps becoming mostly cloudy
OL,11,Ftowards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,14,Fdrizzle, especially along southern
OL,15,Fcoastal districts and hills. Becoming
OL,16,Fdrier and brighter in the afternoon.
OL,17,FVery warm and humid. Chance of
OL,18,Fisolated thunderstorms by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
