OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Ffine with some sunshine. Turning very
OL,7,Fwarm or locally hot, and feeling humid
OL,8,Ftowards the weekend. Staying mainly
OL,9,Fdry, but with a small chance of
OL,10,Fthunderstorms.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
